{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.400", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Frau D\u00f6rner, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe gedacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.800", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man von der moralischen Palme aus einen besseren \u00dcberblick hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich kann das bei Ihnen nicht konstatieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben \u00fcber Sorgen und N\u00f6te theoretisch gesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben dann Dinge ausgef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.160", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nach meiner Einsch\u00e4tzung die Menschen in unserem Land nicht umtreiben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Menschen auf mehr Werbung f\u00fcr Abtreibungen warten und auf theoretische Debatten \u00fcber eine B\u00fcrgerversicherung hoffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.120", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Menschen erwarten vielmehr konkrete Gesundheitspolitik zum Beispiel zur Versorgung des l\u00e4ndlichen Raums oder zur Pflege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Minister hat vorhin unser Konzept vorgestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00e4tten Sie zugeh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4tten Sie es mitbekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber will ich nun reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne darauf hinzuweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.360", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir in der letzten Legislaturperiode gemacht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir die Pflege gest\u00e4rkt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.000", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir im Bereich der Krankenhausstruktur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.920", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei Hospiz- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Palliativversorgung und der Hygiene im Krankenhaus verbessert haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das haben wir gemeinsam miteinander beschlossen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.720", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestatten Sie mir an dieser Stelle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.600", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ich den Gl\u00fcckwunsch an den neuen Minister verbinde mit einem Dank an Hermann Gr\u00f6he, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.400", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seinen Vorg\u00e4nger."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Thema l\u00e4ndlicher Raum ist in der Tat ein kompliziertes Thema. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.320", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen hier viele Verwerfungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich nicht so einfach aufl\u00f6sen lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben viele Ans\u00e4tze: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verbesserte Kooperation der Akteure, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.720", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aufwertung nicht\u00e4rztlicher Gesundheitsberufe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Telemedizin und finanzielle Anreize. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.080", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All diese Themen sind wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber entscheidend wird am Schluss sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00c4rztinnen und \u00c4rzte zu motivieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich im l\u00e4ndlichen Bereich niederzulassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.840", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir f\u00fcr Flexibilit\u00e4t sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.080", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn das Niederlassen im l\u00e4ndlichen Bereich keine unumkehrbare Lebensentscheidung ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die \u00c4rzte auch die Chance haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.800", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich einmal vor Ort umzuschauen und dar\u00fcber nachzudenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.080", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es Sinn macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich im l\u00e4ndlichen Raum niederzulassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das derzeitige Zulassungssystem stellt an dieser Stelle ein Hemmnis dar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bedarfsplanung in ihrer Abstraktheit und Weite ist eher ein Nachteil. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe zu denjenigen geh\u00f6rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in den Koalitionsverhandlungen festgelegt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.800", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das zu reformieren ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.280", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Zukunft wird es keine Zulassungssperren f\u00fcr \u00c4rztinnen und \u00c4rzte mehr geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich in l\u00e4ndlichen oder strukturschwachen Bereichen niederlassen wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist entscheidend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.280", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die \u00c4rzte frei niederlassen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.720", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt Gott sei Dank viele \u00e4ltere \u00c4rzte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weiterhin praktizieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dennoch altersbedingt ihren Patientendurchlauf reduzieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.840", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn diese \u00c4rzte dann nicht mehr praktizieren k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.120", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "soll pl\u00f6tzlich wie Deus ex Machina ein junger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "frischer Arzt bereitstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.000", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der sich vorher nicht hat niederlassen d\u00fcrfen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meinem Wahlkreis wurde zwei jungen Fach\u00e4rztinnen eine zus\u00e4tzliche Zulassung versagt mit dem Hinweis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.680", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es 30\u00a0Kilometer weiter einen Arzt gleicher Fachrichtung gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dessen Wartezimmer noch relativ leer ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.600", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Patienten werden doch wohl selber entscheiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.360", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu welchem Arzt sie gehen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden jedenfalls alles tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.040", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um von dieser Planwirtschaft wegzukommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.120", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hin zur Niederlassungsfreiheit gerade im l\u00e4ndlichen Bereich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.080", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich halte das f\u00fcr ganz entscheidend."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachdem die Kollegin von der FDP das Thema Apotheken vorhin so leidenschaftlich angesprochen hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.600", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "will ich Ihnen auch sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.360", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit Verlaub, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie sich anschauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.400", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was der Onlinehandel mit dem Einzelhandel gemacht hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.240", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wenn Sie daraus Ihre Schl\u00fcsse ziehen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.760", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann werden Sie zu dem Ergebnis kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir an dieser Stelle nicht eingreifen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.280", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "irgendwann richtige Schwierigkeiten mit der Apothekenstruktur bekommen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.320", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Ihnen das nicht gef\u00e4llt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sage ich Ihnen an dieser Stelle auch noch einmal ganz klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben die Chance gehabt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.560", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in einer Regierung mitzugestalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.840", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Chance haben Sie des Effekts wegen einfach so beiseitegeschoben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.480", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Nachteil, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.840", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie jetzt in der Opposition sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.160", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.480", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie an dieser Stelle nur schimpfen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.480", 
